\f0\b Accuracy
\f1\b0 : Measures the overall correctness of the model\'e2\'80\'99s predictions.\
- 
\f0\b Confusion Matrix
\f1\b0 : Visualizes the number of true positives, true negatives, false positives, and false negatives.\
- 
\f0\b Classification Report
\f1\b0 : Provides detailed performance metrics such as precision, recall, and F1-score for both classes (high-risk and low-risk).\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
The model achieved strong performance in terms of accuracy, with a detailed breakdown available through the classification report.\
